metadata.description: The Whaley Golf Club is an NFT project consisting of 101 handmade characters based on Whaley. Whaley Golf is building a real life golf clothing and accessory brand. Holders of Whaley NFTs have access to royalties from any merchandise sales depicting their respective NFT's Whaley design, theme, pattern, etc. Owning a Whaley also gives you access to an exclusive club of holders with added value over time, with full transparency on the Ethereum blockchain.
